to the first solver of each non-sample puzzle.
to the participant with the highest total points:
- Out of all the puzzles (Grand Prize)
- Out of the Challenge Puzzles (Challenge Prize)
- Out of the Beginner Puzzles (Beginner Prize)
- Out of the Abstract Puzzles (Abstract Prize)
The first person to solve a puzzle gets 100 standard points.
The second gets 99 standard points, and so on.
After 99 users have solved a puzzle,
A single user cannot win more than one Puzzle Prize a month,
and cannot win more than one Total Prize.
Prizes are offered as either a gift card (Australia only) or as
a donation on the prizewinner's behalf to a nominated charity
